title: 820-3462 no chime no display
message: This could literally be anything and isn't going to be easy if even possible to solve Bad PCH, cracked ball under PCH, cracked trace/via somewhere, bad CPU, bad solder ball under CPU. Even if the RAM were bad/had cracked solder ball you should get a light on the mouse. I would look under a microscope to see if anything had fallen off of it or received physical damage but in terms of what to measure/look for I have nothing.
